Our #wfh plans took full effect and  as a team we have not returned to our office since then. Except for the odd one or two occasions where someone had to pop in for something. It’s been such a welcomed change that we are not even sure if we will go back to full time office work.

Last year this time after a full week of crisis management planning in the event of a covid case in out office, I called my boss to say my flatmate has tested positive for #COVID. We had to advance our plans and the entire office was closed, cleaned and since then we’ve been #wfh

@Tweet_Dec We got Teams as part of my work's IT upgrade in February 2020. After a training session on how to use it my thoughts were "Well I'll never use this". How wrong was that!! 😊 #WFH

Our #wfh plans took full effect and  as a team we have not returned to our office since then. Except for the odd one or two occasions where someone had to pop in for something. It’s been such a welcomed change that we are not even sure if we will go back to full time office work.

Last year this time after a full week of crisis management planning in the event of a covid case in out office, I called my boss to say my flatmate has tested positive for #COVID. We had to advance our plans and the entire office was closed, cleaned and since then we’ve been #wfh
One full year of #WFH
